metadata.name: LA CORRIDA
metadata.description:
"Everything is physical in all species: It's not the ox that fights, it's the bull!"                                                          
                                               VOLTAIRE

Considered by aficionados and many of its historians as an art, bullfighting has inspired many creators in painting, literature, music and cinema.
However, in a context where opposition to bullfighting is gaining ground, many of its opponents equate it with torture offered in show, and demand its prohibition.

creation on canvas, acrylic paint modified with POWERDIRECTOR ( cyberlink ) for the addition of smoke effect!
